Trust me this is not your ordinary Mehendi look ( My bride’s to be ) 🌸

The look is bold yet balanced. The eyes are the focal point, with a dramatic winged eyeliner and smoky eyeshadow in shades of bronze and gold, accentuating the eyes’ shape. 

 A soft pink blush on the cheeks adds a natural flush, complementing the outfit’s color palette. The lips are painted in a vibrant pink shade, matching the floral accents in the outfit and accessories, creating a cohesive look🩷

The overall makeup enhances the festive vibe while keeping it elegant. A big thanks to the team for this amazing results 🫶🏻
